data.title: Lucrare de Atestat
data.meta_description: Lucrare de atestat - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides biographical information about four famous British actors: Hugh Grant, Anthony Hopkins, Sean Connery, and Laurence Olivier. It discusses their early lives, careers, acting styles, and personal lives. It focuses most on Hugh Grant, providing details about his ancestry, early acting jobs, breakthrough role in Four Weddings and a Funeral, and romantic relationships over the years.
